site_name: City Business CentreLower RoadLondonSouthwarkSE16 2XB
description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide: one mixed-use building of up to 17 storeys in height (including plant screen), with a single basement, comprising 216 purpose-built shared living units and communal amenity space (Sui Generis) and 1,517 square meters of commercial floorspace (Use Class E); one mixed-use building of up to 10 storeys in height, with a single basement, comprising 24 homes and communal amenity space (Use Class C3) and 149.6 square meters of commercial floorspace (Use Class E); and public realm, including play space, as well as other associated works.
